    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood, the S54 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated Double VANOS system, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing OEM+ components. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Finished in a concours-level exterior with zero oxidation or mechanical lash, this example has been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy, ensuring the rod bearings and VANOS hub meet the most stringent tolerances.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Pristine condition. Zero scratches. Original paint. Interior smells new. Full service records included. No mechanical issues.",
