      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into perfection with this pristine example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and kept in a climate-controlled environment. The paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the leather remains supple and untouched, still carrying that elusive new-car scent. Every mechanical component has been serviced ahead of schedule at the dealership, with full documentation provided. Not a single scratch, dent, or blemish can be found on the exterior or the curb-free alloy wheels. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
